highlights.text: “Baller - nowifi Remix” by Abor & Tynna and nowifi is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Global at #13.
“Love Me Not” by Ravyn Lenae has been on Viral Songs Global the longest, at 98 days straight.
Sleep Token has the most spots on Viral Songs Global. “Gethsemane” is the highest at #36.
“P do Pecado - Ao Vivo” by Grupo Menos É Mais and Simone Mendes is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Global, up 13 spots at #26.
